- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is also likely as the paper discusses strategies in functional programs. 
- cs.SE (Software Engineering) is a possible category as the paper addresses the coherence between deduction and computation in strategies. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as strategies are often used in AI applications such as game playing. 
- cs.FL (Formal Languages and Automata Theory) is a less likely category but still relevant as the paper deals with formalizing concepts in rewriting.
